text: Very affordable kway chap set, aunty is nice and polite. Selling at 2.50, wonder how she earns with todays prices.

Please do not eat the kuay chap here. Very expensive for the quality and quantity! Unless you are willing to spend $34 for 2 x large intestines, 2 pax braised pork + tau pork + pig skins + 2 x kuay.
When asked to calculate, she informed that the large intestines are $16.

Very good price and value. Friendly auntie
2.50 per set as in photo. Where to find?
Please come and try
Value worth kway chap. No way can find $2.50 kway chap. Started since 1974 till now, very old school! Must support local hawker!
